    "body": "To give you an accurate quote and make the most of a call, it helps to have a few things sorted first: print-ready artwork (AI, SVG or PNG), an idea of placements and sizes, and a rough budget. We've got guides and tips on our site—check them out, then come back when you're ready. Or leave your details below and we'll send you a quick checklist and follow up when the time's right."
